Package: councildown
Title: Visual Styling for New York City Council Reports
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: person("Nick", "Solomon", 
    email = "nsolomon@council.nyc.gov", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package facilitates the creation of PDF and HTML reports for the
    New York City Council's data scientists. It also includes various useful
    functions for visually styling plots made with ggplot2 and maps made with
    leaflet.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: bookdown,
    ggplot2,
    leaflet,
    sf,
    htmltools,
    htmlwidgets,
    magrittr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
